{"tid":488543,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"分享蘇格蘭高地鐵路攝影","createTime":"2017-12-03T21:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T10:16:15.000Z","uid":121079,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b9228cb5984c1fbccd16c8757513f375e6e49753","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T21:46:06.000Z","msg":"前兩日到Scotland Highland嘅Aviemore旅遊，<br />\n去咗坐英國最高嘅鐵路 -&ldquo;Cairngorm Mountain Railway&rdquo;，山上車站約在海拔1,100米高，<br />\n冬季長期積雪，當日山上氣温約零下10度，<br />\n唔算太凍，不過能見度好低，<br />\n車站職員都建議我唔好離開車站太遠。<br />\n當日嘅乘客主要係到山頂滑雪落山，<br />\n所以回程時有機會在車頭拍下<br />\n&rdquo;driver&rsquo;s view&rdquo; 嘅影片。<br />\n￼<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ml_L-8PMktA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMl_L-8PMktA&d=Sz9Z6jrxRbOMhRsQ2l3tXJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f6562ef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ml_L-8PMktA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/053534_2795cdd2d801b2f07e0de8cd9dd19415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F053534_2795cdd2d801b2f07e0de8cd9dd19415.jpg&h=996933ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/053535_71505cb242283479b296e077715d3bf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F053535_71505cb242283479b296e077715d3bf8.jpg&h=b116e6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/053536_6584452b9d7040d529e98778da0442bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F053536_6584452b9d7040d529e98778da0442bf.jpg&h=e7e77c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外在Aviemore剛好踫到名為<br />\n&ldquo;Santa Express&rdquo;嘅蒸氣火車班次，<br />\n火車頭係1895年英國Glasgow生產嘅0-6-0。<br />\n車上有聖誕老人，車票包聖誕小食及飲品。<br />\n本來我都想去坐吓，不過一早已full booked...<br />\n<br />\n下面段片係近距離拍攝火車開出情況，<br />\n火車頭經過時，司機還向我打了招呼！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SJOgKAZmkT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSJOgKAZmkT8&d=Sz9Z6jrxRbOMhRsQ2l3tXJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=87602bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SJOgKAZmkT8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/053939_def2cb10cf6d53ef87c40681275768bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F053939_def2cb10cf6d53ef87c40681275768bf.jpg&h=a9004e01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/053940_d6732cbef0c4ae1aa07b93829568a26d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F053940_d6732cbef0c4ae1aa07b93829568a26d.jpg&h=6ca42dcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dae90d9a99be1963bde9e8e5dcfeb2f7a0d5d625","tid":488543,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"more <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5814db7845bdbf0c94045927b5d2d77e22f6560","tid":488543,"uid":22559,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"風景係唔錯 不過樓主影相技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447d00cf7c07977c5c22a8d4f9b12ef7b9d9099d","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風景係唔錯 不過樓主影相技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇帶相機，用iPhone6影係咁上吓....<br />\n另外，因為天氣凍，一攞部電話出嚟，電量就不停咁跌，影相係要同時間比賽。係山頂影咗幾張相後，電量已經由90%跌到得40%...."},{"pid":"f9a0cda121cb3a315edffbb1873457c8527ee324","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>more <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夜啲share係Inverness嘅遊記出來"},{"pid":"151ca3568e1a7fa7f74edf7adad675babccdcf56","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5fee926cae77c07b03d79090dafbf24f12e78b","tid":488543,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:48:28.000Z","msg":"點講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明白天氣呢樣野無得強求, 但睇完條片同D相, 真係唔知睇左D乜, 水墨畫咁<br />\n<br />\n見到樓上話風景係唔錯, 想問點睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7388d0d6c7855d8e7bad8cb3b5767e98e597dd8e","tid":488543,"uid":12176,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"唔好侮辱攝影呢個term..."},{"pid":"27bd2930fac5f2a1a831d8ed3880d1f334b90f19","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好侮辱攝影呢個term...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我真係要講句sorry，我中文唔好用錯term..<br />\n下次我用遊記啦"},{"pid":"dd33e05c6be2f71398d2e99e66becd1d54df78bd","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明白天氣呢樣野無得強求, 但睇完條片同D相, 真係唔知睇左D乜, 水墨畫咁<br />\n<br />\n見到樓上話風景係唔錯, 想問點睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，浪費咗你嘅data"},{"pid":"e72cbc6dcb7dd71bfcab826c57add5b532348e6d","tid":488543,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明白天氣呢樣野無得強求, 但睇完條片同D相, 真係唔知睇左D乜, 水墨畫咁<br />\n<br />\n見到樓上話風景係唔錯, 想問點睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，浪費咗你嘅data</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔會，只不過都好慘，咁遠去到睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96584a721f8bc415b259ab359b8973aa8b8e5f5e","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明白天氣呢樣野無得強求, 但睇完條片同D相, 真係唔知睇左D乜, 水墨畫咁<br />\n<br />\n見到樓上話風景係唔錯, 想問點睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，浪費咗你嘅data</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔會，只不過都好慘，咁遠去到睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好天同唔好天，係有唔同嘅體驗。<br />\n十年前我去旅行係喜歡食同睇風景，<br />\n家陣我係追求experience，<br />\n同比較深入認識當地歷史同風土民情。<br />\n好似蒸氣火車咁，我未試過火車頭係旁開過，<br />\n開車上雪山都係一種體驗。"},{"pid":"e3e8f0daf1e0b0a631063a9ddc261d53928ed38d","tid":488543,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會有多D相"},{"pid":"c0ae96410a8568bfdf72cae0c93466263bc61987","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會有多D相</blockquote><br />\n過多陣會分享多一啲旅途雜影。<br />\n<br />\n另外想問有冇outlander / Jame Fraser 嘅fans?<br />\n其實Scotland 我去過好多次，<br />\n而今次去Scotland 係有一半目的係朝聖......"},{"pid":"8f64a444713e45ca91c5dfea10252034266bdb9c","tid":488543,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:25:16.000Z","msg":"Highland <br />\nIsle of Skye <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794dd6e83c18090dcfeb2bb9bf34dc836f5385f4","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T19:03:26.000Z","msg":"係Glasgow落機後，首先去咗10幾分鐘車程嘅Riverside Museum。我之前去過呢間博物館，所以冇乜影相，但呢間博物館真係值得推介，佢嘅規模唔細，裡面又有好多舊巴士，舊火車頭，仲有懷舊街景，同有隻Tall Ship帆船，可以近距離接觸，但係免費入場!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/030310_617d068c869643db4adf88251656be3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F030310_617d068c869643db4adf88251656be3b.jpg&h=f24b0024&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/030312_2d379e4e6abb1257adbc66b45b78c197.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F030312_2d379e4e6abb1257adbc66b45b78c197.jpg&h=81b2e448&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/030314_ee81fc81b026087a920f1f8c1e925d81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F030314_ee81fc81b026087a920f1f8c1e925d81.jpg&h=c8759dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/030315_1ce6b17c60e146a10c8665a27cffc9e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F030315_1ce6b17c60e146a10c8665a27cffc9e0.jpg&h=0ec43870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ff9065fa6f6329410b83afcfef85718ede11654","tid":488543,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T19:48:24.000Z","msg":"真係亂影嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53507e19fae89b19a73858117997cc8395ee90d8","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T20:00:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係亂影嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔識影相，我亦唔係為咗影相而去旅行。<br />\nInstead，我係要體驗當下，影相只係為咗記錄底當時自己嘅感覺。"},{"pid":"3cecb881eba540c6ba09c129d1296e5f91de835c","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T23:24:38.000Z","msg":"第一晚酒店book咗係山卡啦 - Ballachish<br />\n由Glasgow直接開車去要兩粒幾鐘，<br />\n<br />\n不過中途加插2個地方，Loch Fyne同Kilmartin，所以第一日開咗差不多4粒鐘車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/071727_2d830edefc13678aed55009b382242eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F071727_2d830edefc13678aed55009b382242eb.jpg&h=a68418ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n離開Riverside Museum 已經係中午，開咗一粒鐘車去Loch Fyne食lunch，沿途風景優美，但因為我揸緊車，旁邊嗰個又瞓咗，冇相...，不過回港後，會download車Cam啲video再share。<br />\n<br />\nLoch Fyne係一個深長形嘅淺海灣，三面環山，環境清幽，盛產青口，蠔同三文魚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/072038_771b91b2fbd2fee96670cf45453e389a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F072038_771b91b2fbd2fee96670cf45453e389a.jpg&h=539f4c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該區常住人口應該得幾十人，方圚幾十公里只有一間cafe同一間自己牌子嘅seafood oyster bar，最後決定去食seafood。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/072207_b485088ec8d9f92edfb4314137b5f19c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F072207_b485088ec8d9f92edfb4314137b5f19c.jpg&h=1706d0b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\norder咗細青口，半打蠔同fish and chips，找數廿幾pounds，全部物有所值！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/072248_5e14a89ab400a87518fe7c74adb66b6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F072248_5e14a89ab400a87518fe7c74adb66b6c.jpg&h=e5689cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/072305_dd2883ff7bf5700efa28e1c954687ba5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F072305_dd2883ff7bf5700efa28e1c954687ba5.jpg&h=b8975efa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27a3bc059c105dd9fd853ef91d50ae3274307cb4","tid":488543,"uid":21622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T23:33:02.000Z","msg":"Scotland <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d229d5b1bffbff98c5919a8ae5ac4715fec1b8","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T00:28:26.000Z","msg":"改正，午餐找數應該係三十幾磅。<br />\n<br />\n食完lunch已經成兩點，趕路去下一個目的地Kilmartin Museum。雖然條山路可以行成百Km/h，但係沿路不時有慢車拉龍，去到已經三點幾，差不多日落，只可以行個Museum同旁邊嘅standing stones，去唔到比較遠嘅stone circle。<br />\n<br />\nKilmartin係位於蘇格蘭以至全英國，新石器時代到青銅時代嘅出土文物最集中的區域。而Kilmartin 另一個出名之處係一個名為Nether Largie嘅石陣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/082236_a7dd3dbc1306f81920fcace2ecb7883b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F082236_a7dd3dbc1306f81920fcace2ecb7883b.jpg&h=265cf268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/082458_696f23588ced57617424489fbcb2bc21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F082458_696f23588ced57617424489fbcb2bc21.jpg&h=610f763d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/082459_fe70ce87b17c7855527ca7880e44b957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F082459_fe70ce87b17c7855527ca7880e44b957.jpg&h=354d7572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個石陣有另於英格蘭Salisbury嘅Stonehenge，詳情可以上網search，不作多介紹。不過我去睇standing stones嘅另一原因係&rdquo;Outlander&rdquo;，有睇過就應該知道點解！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/082817_4ea2ce4f46c5a09255c5d645b0f388d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F082817_4ea2ce4f46c5a09255c5d645b0f388d8.jpg&h=94ce7f98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"910d1bc30f0abe364338026bce345bd64d6d712a","tid":488543,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:03:44.000Z","msg":"個石陣無得埋去架?"},{"pid":"4d602390153163662fa39d55b1473ecbb66ee9dc","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"睇完石陣差不多4點，個天已黑，去Oban Tesco買返啲零食後，馬上趕去Ballachulish 洒店攞。<br />\n呢間酒店係由一間17世紀古堡改建，由18世紀開始已經有傳聞鬧鬼，甚至話有人影到鬼相.......不過唔駛一千蚊有行政房(唔係傳聞嗰三間鬼房)，仲包早晩兩餐，夜晚嗰餐仲係3 course meal，真係理鬼得佢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090525_303d03f5216264cb0d63ff08fb437986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090525_303d03f5216264cb0d63ff08fb437986.jpg&h=596de398&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090527_260322b92dc4e035bbe03f03fb52ec35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090527_260322b92dc4e035bbe03f03fb52ec35.jpg&h=feddbe85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間洒店外面環境一流，嗰朝因為時差關係，5點醒咗，之後出咗洒店外面行morning walk，望上天空，啲星比太空館天象廰開場嗰幕仲要多好很多，勁誇張！<br />\n<br />\n早餐buffet有Scotland 特產Haggis，味道同香港嘅牛雜差不多，幾好食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090625_6454106c482e10c0c45c9a1743040193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090625_6454106c482e10c0c45c9a1743040193.jpg&h=f1cd9b21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日出後發現四週山頂都已經蓋上白雪，好靚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090740_3703dc965478020d1a1c0b8813339bf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090740_3703dc965478020d1a1c0b8813339bf0.jpg&h=b468f5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090742_437eccc146399f28a0d36c3ba8f62807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090742_437eccc146399f28a0d36c3ba8f62807.jpg&h=56127d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090743_77ac4a0d2a2cc299110b7a2cd6df8fc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090743_77ac4a0d2a2cc299110b7a2cd6df8fc1.jpg&h=66dbb2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一日完<br />\n如果喜歡這遊記的記，請記得比近隻手指公！<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 聽日坐夜船去荷蘭，冇Internet"},{"pid":"cc5caec95c09d83d7afccd536c3834a4a84452cc","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個石陣無得埋去架?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係可以入去，嗰個閘係防止啲羊走出來"},{"pid":"62fc30fc20919f098d512ac19ca7a32de14b8556","tid":488543,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係亂影嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔識影相，我亦唔係為咗影相而去旅行。<br />\nInstead，我係要體驗當下，影相只係為咗記錄底當時自己嘅感覺。</blockquote><br />\n啱,有時記憶/親身經歷重要過相,有時睇返D相都唔記得自己影過,反而親身經歷過左幾年仲記得"},{"pid":"d305a9dbccfe7a0b8435a6a12bc5b049b3c9da10","tid":488543,"uid":33777,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好侮辱攝影呢個term...</blockquote><br />\n屌你收啦,你自己影得好好咩<br />\n攝影都可以係自己留紀錄一種,一定要影得好先可以出遊記/用攝影做標題?<br />\n人地出遊記你唔鍾意咪唔好撚睇囉<br />\n講到好似收左你入場費迫你睇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a180cf524adb3467a71ae72ec25ec2286b49fc9","tid":488543,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風景係唔錯 不過樓主影相技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講你睇好多遊記有幾多個D相真係靚,咪又係當紀錄做分享<br />\n再者只係其他人出遊記一定出D靚相俾你睇,唔通出柒相趕客咩"},{"pid":"eb050fd78052ae03d40bac45f74312d3b77bc3e6","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係亂影嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔識影相，我亦唔係為咗影相而去旅行。<br />\nInstead，我係要體驗當下，影相只係為咗記錄底當時自己嘅感覺。</blockquote><br />\n啱,有時記憶/親身經歷重要過相,有時睇返D相都唔記得自己影過,反而親身經歷過左幾年仲記得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗起「白日夢冒險王」(The Secret life of Walter Mitty) 裡面嘅一幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/144124_b7462408c606a6971b35f6fc58cf04a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F144124_b7462408c606a6971b35f6fc58cf04a5.jpg&h=0c527de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實家陣好多人忘記咗去旅行嘅本意。"},{"pid":"27456a230424665e52e479404bf521fd24a57041","tid":488543,"uid":44377,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"咁又要扯到去旅行的意義?<br />\n你鍾意用眼睛去感受, 人地鍾意用相機去紀錄, 有話分咩旅行的本義?<br />\n去旅行自己鍾意點玩咪點玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3e18af6de76c3ea297fad291699330ba66bd81","tid":488543,"uid":121079,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁又要扯到去旅行的意義?<br />\n你鍾意用眼睛去感受, 人地鍾意用相機去紀錄, 有話分咩旅行的本義?<br />\n去旅行自己鍾意點玩咪點玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係講開又講啫，純粹個人見解<br />\n<br />\n其實你講嘅嘢我好認同，<br />\n不過我唔會係旅行嘅時候，<br />\n花好多心機時間去為咗影幅相，<br />\n而錯過咗一啲重要嘅moment。<br />\n<br />\n就好似係夜晚睇星嘅時候，<br />\n我會放低部相機，靜心欣賞。<br />\n有部份人或會用相機記錄低當時嘅天空，<br />\n但係又可能會因爲過份專注影相，<br />\n錯過了一啲流星。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲嘢冇話對與錯，<br />\n不過我會尊重其他人嘅取向。"},{"pid":"aa231b147525e5b4c5e648dff89cfcc927583704","tid":488543,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁又要扯到去旅行的意義?<br />\n你鍾意用眼睛去感受, 人地鍾意用相機去紀錄, 有話分咩旅行的本義?<br />\n去旅行自己鍾意點玩咪點玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n旅遊台講下冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65262a063a7b1604170de5d9cfdcb3b0e8952a61","tid":488543,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁又要扯到去旅行的意義?<br />\n你鍾意用眼睛去感受, 人地鍾意用相機去紀錄, 有話分咩旅行的本義?<br />\n去旅行自己鍾意點玩咪點玩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係講開又講啫，純粹個人見解<br />\n<br />\n其實你講嘅嘢我好認同，<br />\n不過我唔會係旅行嘅時候，<br />\n花好多心機時間去為咗影幅相，<br />\n而錯過咗一啲重要嘅moment。<br />\n<br />\n就好似係夜晚睇星嘅時候，<br />\n我會放低部相機，靜心欣賞。<br />\n有部份人或會用相機記錄低當時嘅天空，<br />\n但係又可能會因爲過份專注影相，<br />\n錯過了一啲流星。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲嘢冇話對與錯，<br />\n不過我會尊重其他人嘅取向。</blockquote><br />\n我覺得啦, 每個人去旅行想做既事唔同, 唔好再話咩旅行的本意<br />\n花好多心機時間去影幅相就係唔想錯過想影果個moment, 你係要話會錯過左其他重要既moment就算啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然你自稱話D野無對與錯, 但你係咁強調掛住影相會MISS左其他野, 你心目中都分左高低啦, 去旅行自己玩得開心就OK, 無話邊樣野高級D, 唔駛強調咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda4eda586b6cd1324234fe9c9a4eeec7e3c2e5f","tid":488543,"uid":50500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"鉄膠會明白的<br />\n<br />\n辛辛苦苦去到, 其實全日或者係成個TRIP 只係得果幾十分鐘或幾分鐘的精華<br />\n我相信各鉄膠會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦晒!!"},{"pid":"81bc3d64f3521dfe06f6dc7001454511ad778fca","tid":488543,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:51: